2026-02-26T19:04:28.5054423Z         ############################
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5054513Z         # Package would be ignored #
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5054582Z         ############################
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5054886Z         Python recognizes 'botocore.data.xray' as an importable package[^1],
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5055144Z         but it is absent from setuptools' `packages` configuration.
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5055153Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5055508Z         This leads to an ambiguous overall configuration. If you want to distribute this
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5055832Z         package, please make sure that 'botocore.data.xray' is explicitly added
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056000Z         to the `packages` configuration field.
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056008Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056257Z         Alternatively, you can also rely on setuptools' discovery methods
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056445Z         (for example by using `find_namespace_packages(...)`/`find_namespace:`
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056598Z         instead of `find_packages(...)`/`find:`).
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056606Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056960Z         You can read more about "package discovery" on setuptools documentation page:
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5056970Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5057306Z         - https://setuptools.pypa.io/en/latest/userguide/package_discovery.html
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5057315Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5057578Z         If you don't want 'botocore.data.xray' to be distributed and are
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5057819Z         already explicitly excluding 'botocore.data.xray' via
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5058104Z         `find_namespace_packages(...)/find_namespace` or `find_packages(...)/find`,
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5058303Z         you can try to use `exclude_package_data`, or `include-package-data=False` in
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5058473Z         combination with a more fine grained `package-data` configuration.
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5058483Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5058820Z         You can read more about "package data files" on setuptools documentation page:
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5058826Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059008Z         - https://setuptools.pypa.io/en/latest/userguide/datafiles.html
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059013Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059017Z 
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059185Z         [^1]: For Python, any directory (with suitable naming) can be imported,
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059303Z               even if it does not contain any `.py` files.
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059464Z               On the other hand, currently there is no concept of package data
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059600Z               directory, all directories are treated like packages.
2026-02-26T19:04:28.5059719Z         ********************************************************************************
